The paper discusses the analysis and mining of big data, which is a common topic in the database (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of tools like Pandas, Numpy, STATA, and SPSS also suggests a focus on data analysis and statistics, which could fall under the information retrieval (cs.IR) and social and information networks (cs.SI) sub-categories. Finally, the mention of productivity and automation could also relate to the computer engineering (cs.CE) sub-category.
